nepali is a tamil film neo noir romantic psychological thriller film written and directed by v.z.durai .   the featuring bharath and meera jasmine in the lead roles , released in 2008 .   bharath plays three different roles in the movie .   the film has music by srikanth deva and was shot in ooty , chennai and hyderabad .   the film was released on april 10 , 2008 .   the movie was panned by the critics and bombed at the box office .